Title: Authorizes the town of Ithaca, county of Tompkins to discontinue as parklands and alienate certain lands
Summary: Authorizes the town of Ithaca, county of Tompkins, to discontinue as parklands and alienate certain lands for the purpose of providing needed resources to the existing parks within such town.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the town of Ithaca to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands
